+        If ``-1``, then the number of jobs is set to the number of CPU cores.
+
+    Returns
+    -------
+    core_sample_indices_ : array, shape (n_core_samples,)
+        The indices of the core samples.
+
+    labels_ : array, shape (n_samples,)
+        The estimated labels.
+
+    See also
+    --------
+    OPTICS
